OL,3,CLes Creux Bowls Club to close due to
OL,4,C'too few members' and 'high costs'
OL,6,FClub Secretary John Mallet says the
OL,7,Fdecision to close is down to high
OL,8,Fcosts and dwindling membership:
OL,9,F"There's too few members to carry on
OL,10,Fand if you have a wander around the
OL,11,Fbuilding and the grounds you can see
OL,12,Fwhat a huge entity it is to maintain.
OL,14,F"I think we have 18 bowlers at the
OL,15,Fminute on the books, but probably half
OL,16,Fhave various ailments which means
OL,17,Fthey're just going to stop bowling."
OL,19,FThe club was established to host
OL,20,Finternational tournaments such as the
OL,21,FEuropean Championships in 2001.
