OL,3,CLes Creux Bowls Club to close due to
OL,4,C'too few members' and 'high costs'
OL,6,FHowever, over the years, it has become
OL,7,Fdifficult to get competitions to take
OL,8,Fplace at the venue and the number of
OL,9,Fmembers has fallen, prompting the
OL,10,Fclub's decision not to renew its lease.
OL,12,FRichard Collinson, a member of 20
OL,13,Fyears, has described the closure as
OL,14,F"tragic".
OL,16,FHe explained: "Often during the winter
OL,17,Fpeople play up here from various clubs
OL,18,Fbecause this is a 3G pitch, it's an
OL,19,Foutdoor service and the majority of
OL,20,Fthe clubs are on grass so they close
OL,21,Fin the winter.
