OL,3,CLes Creux Bowls Club to close due to
OL,4,C'too few members' and 'high costs'
OL,6,F"It's a good facility and it's an
OL,7,Fopportunity for people who are in
OL,8,Fretirement age and people over 80.
OL,9,FChatting all the time and sociably,
OL,10,Fit's really good for everybody's
OL,11,Fwellbeing."
OL,13,FThe decision to close the club was
OL,14,Ffirst made in 2022 and then confirmed
OL,15,Fin 2023.
OL,17,FIt will shut for the final time on
OL,18,FSaturday 30 March.
