OL,3,CLes Creux Bowls Club to close due to
OL,4,C'too few members' and 'high costs'
OL,6,FClub member Jenny Robinson said she
OL,7,Fwas "really sad" about the club's
OL,8,Fclosure
OL,10,FShe added: "We've been coming up here
OL,11,Fever since the winter started so it's
OL,12,Fbeen an absolute godsend to get out in
OL,13,Fthe fresh air.
OL,15,F"I can't think of another game where a
OL,16,F70, 80 or 90-year-old could compete
OL,17,Fagainst a 20-year-old and win.
